\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Arthropod - armor plating. Expressionless eyes.  Too many legs jointed in too many places.  Abdomen pulses, antennae twitch, tiny oral appendages shift food to the mouth. Lean a little closer and it leaps into the air, almost into one\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s face, then veers of on crackling wings.}
