\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Butterflies are benign aesthetically pleasing faunal members. }
\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Often flutter thteir weings, even while perched or taking water at puddles.}
