\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Vultures are perfectly adapted for living on carrion. They may have to wait for a few days between meals, so the expend little energy soaring for hours with scarcely a flap of their broad wings. Keen eyesight, well developed sense of smell. Naked heads for tearing into carrion. }
